{"id": 2281, "genre": 1001, "title": "初到一个城市生活的时候，你都是通过啥融入新环境的？", "description": "你也有“到哪儿都像当地人”的特异功能吗？（题图来自：iStock）", "record_count": 2445, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180416102658Xn2hpF5ZHE8WSBRA.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-04-16T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 275968, "content": "怎么算融入?。。就衣食住行的话 逛逛聊聊搜搜就知道了。。归属感 好像生活多少年都没有。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1227251}, {"id": 275970, "content": "以自己住的地方呈中心闲逛，各种巷子，小吃走一走，总是会碰到一些人聊聊天，就慢慢融入了", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 367955}, {"id": 276226, "content": "先找吃的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 789686}, {"id": 277506, "content": "假装跟你很熟，其实我都不知道你是哪位，来来喝一杯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487377}, {"id": 275971, "content": "认识新的人，多结交朋友，换一个态度对待感情", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1317749}, {"id": 276227, "content": "健身房和菜市场", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1318779}, {"id": 275972, "content": "逛逛街，聊聊天。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1256295}, {"id": 278276, "content": "逛超市", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 889204}, {"id": 275973, "content": "吃，喝，玩，乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1299695}, {"id": 275975, "content": "完全无压力", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1296212}, {"id": 275976, "content": "城市里好玩的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1100110}, {"id": 275977, "content": "每周寻找一个这里的好玩的地方，以这个地方为中心闲逛四周", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236175}, {"id": 276234, "content": "我从不融入，保持孤单。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1302622}, {"id": 275979, "content": "找一个可靠的同事或是同学，重点是有相同爱好，出去吃喝玩乐。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1308051}, {"id": 275980, "content": "和本地人交朋友～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1307539}, {"id": 275981, "content": "吃喝玩乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1288774}, {"id": 275982, "content": "貌似是学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315155}, {"id": 275983, "content": "去城市的书店", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 286642}, {"id": 276495, "content": "假装是本地人", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1302027}, {"id": 283407, "content": "下饭店、去公园、图书馆、沙龙活动……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1352126}, {"id": 275984, "content": "足球", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704708}, {"id": 275985, "content": "正常的生活，就好，时间会自己融合", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 96454}, {"id": 275986, "content": "各种被坑…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1293210}, {"id": 283410, "content": "玩着瞧着……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1352126}, {"id": 275987, "content": "以及找工作不顺利", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1293210}, {"id": 275988, "content": "挤早高峰", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1293210}, {"id": 275989, "content": "有老乡就不会觉得陌生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1314739}, {"id": 276247, "content": "说本地方言", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1313552}, {"id": 275994, "content": "书店", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1317843}, {"id": 275995, "content": "去菜市场买菜\n熟悉当地的食材", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1068424}, {"id": 277275, "content": "学习，然后去当地各处玩，吃好吃的东西，默默一个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1322687}, {"id": 275996, "content": "在路上慢悠悠的走，总有人来问路。感觉自己好像融入了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1031737}, {"id": 275997, "content": "骑车是最好的体验城市的方式，去地铁站、便利店和路边小摊最能融入城市。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 677668}, {"id": 276253, "content": "迷路", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 987510}, {"id": 277790, "content": "找工作跟同事去泡小姐姐", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1325717}, {"id": 275999, "content": "融不进的北上广\n回不去的故乡", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 220268}, {"id": 276000, "content": "当然是先看地图，还有一些别的游玩攻略了，专门找有哪些好玩的地方了。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1317872}, {"id": 276002, "content": "菜场买点菜，球场看个比赛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1228841}, {"id": 276003, "content": "到处逛逛，深入了解。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1316699}, {"id": 280867, "content": "学习吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1339478}, {"id": 276004, "content": "走街串巷的拍照", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310638}, {"id": 276516, "content": "通过口音", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 547033}, {"id": 276005, "content": "先找到一家星巴克", "image": "img/option/option/20180416165822foGB4Z15JLAkY0Hw.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855996}, {"id": 276006, "content": "翻墙，和世界人民一个权利，实现精神移民", "image": "img/option/option/20180416165855JBgA8aIKzciZkqrb.jpg", "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 116772}, {"id": 278311, "content": "该干嘛就干嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1328183}, {"id": 276777, "content": "没啥融入不了的，反正宅", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 810373}, {"id": 276522, "content": "去网咖上网", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284170}, {"id": 276525, "content": "不记得，生活就是正常过，陌生人之间变减少了隔阂，多了些温暖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1309082}, {"id": 276015, "content": "逛吃逛吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1316135}, {"id": 276017, "content": "不融入 融不入", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 818091}]}